(15602, 'fluconazole, sodium chloride', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Calcium Channel Blockers Certain dihydropyridine calcium channel antagonists (nifedipine, isradipine, amlodipine, and felodipine) are metabolized by CYP3A4.', 'DailyMed'),
