(22227, 'macitentan and tadalafil', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Clinical pharmacology studies were conducted to assess the effect of tadalafil on the potentiation of the blood–pressure–lowering effects of selected antihypertensive medications (amlodipine, angiotensin II receptor blockers, bendroflumethiazide, enalapril, and metoprolol).', 'DailyMed'),
